xt-slate-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Perguntas sobre medicamentos, check-ins de recuperação, esclarecimentos de resultados</p></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-blue-vibrant/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-activity h-8 w-8 text-blue-vibrant" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">Cuidados Crônicos</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Orientação contínua para diabetes, hipertensão, asma</p></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-purple-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text h-8 w-8 text-purple-accent" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">Segundas Opiniões</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Revise relatórios com segurança e forneça orientação profissional a novos pacientes</p></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-teal-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users h-8 w-8 text-teal-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744"></path><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">Primeiro Contato</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-center leading-relaxed">Inicie relacionamentos seguros e documentados que levam a consultas completas</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Customer Success Stories</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->Allowing doctors to offer telemedicine, remote monitoring health plans, collect payments and the health blog are some of the best features of the Virtual Practice®.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Gerard Saltibus MD</p><p class="text-gray-600">General Practitioner, St. Lucia</p></div></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->Virtual Practice platform is delivering next-generation medical care. As a multidisciplinary team, we find it powerful and intuitive for organizing patient cases, with clear medical records that support precise documentation and effective care.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Georgios Leon - Metabolic Specialist</p><p class="text-gray-600">Precision Medicine Startup, Greece</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is patient messaging in telehealth?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Patient Messaging is a secure, HIPAA/GDPR-compliant way for patients to send health questions to their provider between visits. Unlike live chat, it's asynchronous — providers respond within defined timeframes, not in real time."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Why should my clinic use secure patient messaging instead of SMS or WhatsApp?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"SMS and consumer apps aren't secure, compliant, or integrated into your workflow. Secure patient messaging keeps communication encrypted, linked to each patient's health record, and billable — so providers are fairly compensated for their time."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can providers bill for patient messages?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patient Messaging can be configured as a billable service with provider-specific pricing. Bills are auto-generated, patients pay online, and funds are transferred directly to your clinic's account. You can also configure follow-up notes within each encounter."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does patient messaging integrate with the health record?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Every question and response is stored in the patient's health record, alongside their health tracker data, labs, and consultations. Providers can schedule appointments, create documents, or assign care plans based on the perspective from a message thread."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is this feature useful for second opinions?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patient Messaging is ideal for patients seeking second opinions or initial guidance. New patients submitting questions through your portal are seamlessly onboarded as registered patients in your Virtual Practice."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do notifications work for patient messaging?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Automated notifications are sent at key points: providers receive alerts when a new question arrives, and patients are notified when a response is ready. Notifications can be delivered by email, SMS, or app push."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can patients attach reports or images to their questions?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patients can include lab results, medical reports, or photos with their messages, giving providers richer context when responding."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does patient messaging help prevent patients from relying only on AI tools?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"When patients don't have easy access to their providers, they often turn to search engines or AI tools for answers. Patient Messaging ensures they can reach their own doctor directly — securely, professionally, and with full context from their health record."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is patient messaging only for established patients?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. It's valuable both for existing patients (follow-ups, chronic care, medication questions) and for new patients (initial contact, second opinions). It helps providers grow their patient base while improving continuity of care."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does patient messaging save time for providers?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Because it's asynchronous, providers can respond on their schedule within set response windows. This avoids interruptions from phone calls or SMS, reduces no-shows, and ensures that time spent answering patient questions is properly compensated."}}]}</script><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg 